highlights.text: “Deslocado” by NAPA is the biggest gainer on Viral Songs Hong Kong, up 29 spots at #54.
TENBLANK has the most spots on Viral Songs Hong Kong. “旋律と結晶” is the highest at #10.
“零距离的思念” by TINY 7 has been on Viral Songs Hong Kong the longest, at 148 days straight.
“Somewhere in Between” by Blood Orange is the highest new entry on Viral Songs Hong Kong at #96.
